public class FedmIscTagHandler_EPC_Class1_Gen2_IDS_SL900A
extends FedmIscTagHandler_EPC_Class1_Gen2

Class for HF/UHF transponder EPC Class 1 Generation 2 of manufacturer IDS Microchip .
This class supports only addressed or non-addressed mode in Host-Mode
